            <ol>
                <li>Write your Lua script in the editor above</li>
                <li>Click "PUBLISH SCRIPT" - Your script gets a permanent URL</li>
                <li>Copy the generated loadstring</li>
                <li><strong>In Roblox Executor:</strong>
                    <div class="code-block">Paste: loadstring(game:HttpGet("YOUR_URL_HERE"))()</div>
                </li>
                <li><strong>In Roblox Studio:</strong>
